                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "This aura is good for a speed build on Volt, Nezha, Gauss, or Wisp for a fast dash across missions if sprinting. Combine it with a bullet jump mod like Lightning Dash or Mobilize such that bullet jumping doesn't feel slow, and something like Handspring and Pain Threshold so getting knocked down doesn't affect your Warframe either."
